.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-2::.
The people have 6 different jobs:  photographer, manager, videographer, chef, coach, dressmaker
House: tower, wooden, art-deco, craftsman, townhouse, futuristic
1. the craftsman house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
2. the townhouse house is on the left of the coach##1
3. the craftsman house is between the chef and the photographer##2
4. the videographer is on the right of the wooden house##1
5. the photographer is on the far right##1
6. the townhouse house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
7. the chef is on the right of the tower house##1
8. the manager is on the left of the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |  3   |    4    |   5    |     6      |
| Job   | manager | dressmaker | coach | chef | videographer | photographer  |
| House           | futuristic | townhouse  | tower | wooden    | craftsman  | art-deco |

