.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-3::.
There are 6 different nationalities: polish, british, canadian, argentine, french, egyptian
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: skateboarding, biathlon, soccer, cricket, lacrosse, skiing
1. the polish is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
2. the argentine is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the french##1
5. the canadian is on the far right##1
6. the french is between the argentine and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
8. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the argentine##1
9. the british is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |     3      |   4    |     5      |     6     |
| Nationality         | british | polish | egyptian      | french | argentine | canadian      |
| Sport   | biathlon    | skiing  | skateboarding | cricket   | lacrosse       | soccer |

