.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-4::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, game, tiparillo, davidoff, ritmeester, chaman
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: rose, balloon-flower, azalea, zinnia, sunflower, begonia
1. the person who growsazalea is the davidoff-smoker##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
3. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
4. the person who growszinnia is the game-smoker##1
5. the oliveros-smoker is the person who growsrose##1
6. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person who growsrose and the chaman-smoker##2
7. the game-smoker is on the left of the chaman-smoker##1
8. the person who growsazalea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |   6    |
| Cigar        | game    | chaman | tiparillo | oliveros | ritmeester | davidoff   |
| Flower   | zinnia | sunflower        | balloon-flower  | rose     | begonia  | azalea |

