1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the fan jazz##1
3. the fan indie is on the right of the fan punk##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
5. the fan jazz is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the fan folk is on the left of the fan punk##1
7. the fan gospel is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
8. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3    |   4    |   5   |    6     |
| Hobby   | drawing   | writing    | skydiving | card-games | woodworking | puzzles   |
| Music-Genre         | techno | gospel | jazz | folk | punk  | indie |

