4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far right##1
5. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
6. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who growsamaryllis##1
8. the person who growsazalea is between the person who growsmarigold and the person who's sport is snowboarding##2
