2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the russian##1
3. the russian is between the mexican and the spanish##2
4. the spanish is the person who's birthday is in january##1
5. the japanese is on the left of the spanish##1
6. the mexican is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in june##2
7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
8. the italian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
9. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the indian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |   2    |   3   |    4    |     5     |    6    |
| Nationality       | japanese | spanish | russian | mexican | indian | italian |
| Birthday   | september | january    | june  | april    | august    | may    |

