4. the person who's hobby is camping is the person who likes mauve##1
5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
6. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
8. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
9. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who likes emerald##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Hobby           | camping | reading | traveling | magic-tricks | rock-climbing | drawing |
| Color   | mauve   | grey   | emerald         | purple    | ebony     | apricot     |

