.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-9::.
6 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, whist, bridge, snooker, canasta
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: folk, ambient, country, gospel, blues, house
 1. the person playing canasta is the fan gospel##1
 2. the fan folk is between the person playing backgammon and the fan house##2
 3. the fan ambient is on the far left##1
 4. the fan gospel is the person playing canasta##1
 5. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the fan folk##1
 6. the fan gospel is the person playing canasta##1
 7. the fan country is on the right of the fan gospel##1
 8. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 9. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
10. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2     |     3      |   4    |   5    |       6       |
| Game   | backgammon   | snooker  | scrabble | bridge | canasta | whist     |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | folk | house    | blues | gospel | country |

