.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-14::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: february, march, june, october, december, january
The people use 6 different means of transport: car, boat, bus, bike, train, roller
 1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 2. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the train and the person who's birthday is in march##2
 3. the person driving the train is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person driving the car##2
 4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is between the person driving the bus and the person who's birthday is in june##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is the person driving the boat##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
 8. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |   3    |     4     |       5        |      6       |
| Birthday   | october     | february | december   | june     | january       | march       |
| Transport    | boat | bike   | car | train | roller | bus |

