.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-2-20::.
City: liverpool, berlin, colone, rome, new-york, edinburgh
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: volleyball, cycling, golf, lacrosse, handball, skateboarding
 1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far left##1
 3. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
 4. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 5. the person traveling to colone is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 7. the person who's sport is cycling is the person traveling to colone##1
 8. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 9. the person who's sport is golf is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person traveling to liverpool##2
10. the person traveling to new-york is the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |       5       |    6    |
| City         | rome | liverpool | berlin | edinburgh | new-york | colone |
| Sport   | volleyball | handball | golf      | lacrosse     | skateboarding       | cycling |

 